## Architecture diagram

Batch CSV --> Bronze --> Silver --> Gold --> Dashboard
Live API --> Bronze --> Silver --> Gold --> Dashboard


## Features

- Real-time API ingestion
- Batch data ingestion
- Bronze/Silver/Gold architecture
- Delta tables
- Data cleansing and transformations
- SQL analytics
- Dashboard creation
- Scheduled Databricks jobs

## Tech Stack

- Databricks
- PySpark
- SQL
- Delta Lake
- Open-Meteo API
- GitHub


## How to Run

1. Create Databricks 
2. Upload stores.csv
3. Run bronze ingestion notebook
4. Run silver transformation notebook
5. Run gold analytics notebook
6. Execute dashboard queries
